{"tid":1263840,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［長期抗爭］要杜絕奶共派，就要由根源開始！","createTime":"2019-06-28T11:33:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T07:06:22.000Z","uid":34342,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ddd61ecb821e6b5b21185d67ed8c820766c6e06b","tid":1263840,"uid":34342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T11:33:13.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過點解啲奶共黨可以有源源不絕嘅年輕人入去奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實好多唔同區份既乜傑出學生，優秀學生都係紅底（好多都同禮義廉有關），佢地會透過呢啲途徑招兵買馬，再慢慢筡毒啲學生，最後變埋佢地啲梯隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己之前都係嗰啲學生，成日俾人說你去做善事（幫啲紅底組織賣旗），又會有啲好平嘅晚宴（極多奶共人士贊助獎品），之後仲會叫你做委員，幫手助選之類，諗起就覺得可恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全能嘅巴絲有冇計阻止呢啲紅底育成計劃？<br />\n<br />\n利伸：臨崖勒馬，無accept 到任何紅底offer"},{"pid":"10c7b22169f66ee9dd7fb3936aa71570e288b87f","tid":1263840,"uid":34342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T13:42:16.000Z","msg":"推到有地區工作巴絲睇"},{"pid":"398c1e0b6d32a5237d70a2e2b9561f9810468141","tid":1263840,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T13:45:01.000Z","msg":"你講個啲紅底資優生見一個po一個上連登"},{"pid":"a8f8df610512b25f67cd266d1689c9006bdc9500","tid":1263840,"uid":34342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:06:48.000Z","msg":"其實大部分有諗法嘅都走左，係得翻啲柒嘅係到，但係禮義廉一定照推上去做明日之星，扯線公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571b88b4921fbdd63fbaf410b095a830ea8e47e4","tid":1263840,"uid":34342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:23:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61d85a85c07049fbe3c31e4df5a777f3f7194578","tid":1263840,"uid":34342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T17:10:35.000Z","msg":"有冇地區工作巴打"},{"pid":"2f1a97bd57f57b031de67aaa86ecae247c304684","tid":1263840,"uid":34342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:55:03.000Z","msg":"推，唔想見到天真00後中招"},{"pid":"b0b59a449ca31b0ece3a9cab04595bd5fa1aa443","tid":1263840,"uid":34342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:06:22.000Z","msg":"有冇唔同地區既代表可以一齊推<br />\n小弟個邊係under葛博士個區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}